{"type":"message","id":"c0c77415","parentId":"45339bef","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:09:06.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的主人，我检查一下环境状态哦~ 😊\n\n**环境检查结果：**\n- ✅ **Python**：已安装 3.14.3\n- ✅ **AI 工具**：已检测到 `openclaw` CLI，可以生成智能回复\n- ✅ **配置文件**：已存在，Cookie 已配置\n\n不过...服务好像**没有在运行**呢，PID 文件不存在哦~ 需要我帮你启动服务吗？启动后就可以自动监控消息啦 🐟\n\n对啦，我先给你几个方案选择哦：\n\n**方案1：直接启动监控服务** - 启动后后台自动运行，收到消息会实时通知你，简单问题自动回复\n**方案2：先检查 Cookie 是否有效** - 看看当前 Cookie 会不会过期，没问题再启动\n**方案3：手动查看日志后再决定** - 看看之前运行有没有什么错误\n\n你想选哪个呀？ 💡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773878943282}}
{"type":"message","id":"90127c29","parentId":"c0c77415","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:11:25.611Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5487bc006cb4c3fb9d384f1450f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 08:11 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5487bc006cb4c3fb9d384f1450f]\nou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b: 方案2"}],"timestamp":1773879085609}}
